{"body": "Implementation note: opt-out studies pause enrollment in the action, not in the driver, so this is something we can fix without a system add-on update. This should  be a pretty easy change. The opt-out studies version of this is just a few lines: https://github.com/mozilla/normandy/blob/4a7bf8083cac71b521e909ee3e55bda4c318c67e/recipe-server/client/actions/opt-out-study/index.js#L40-L46", "body_text": "Implementation note: opt-out studies pause enrollment in the action, not in the driver, so this is something we can fix without a system add-on update. This should  be a pretty easy change. The opt-out studies version of this is just a few lines: \n  \n    \n      normandy/recipe-server/client/actions/opt-out-study/index.js\n    \n    \n        Lines 40 to 46\n      in\n      4a7bf80\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n        \n          \n           if (isEnrollmentPaused) { \n        \n\n        \n          \n             this.normandy.log(`Enrollment is paused for recipe ${recipeId}`, 'debug'); \n        \n\n        \n          \n           } else if (hasStudy) { \n        \n\n        \n          \n             this.normandy.log(`Study for recipe ${recipeId} already exists`, 'debug'); \n        \n\n        \n          \n           } else { \n        \n\n        \n          \n             this.normandy.log(`Starting study for recipe ${recipeId}`, 'debug'); \n        \n\n        \n          \n             await studies.start({", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/normandy/issues/comments/337672371", "created_at": "2017-10-18T17:47:39Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "html_url": "https://github.com/mozilla/normandy/issues/1112#issuecomment-337672371", "updated_at": "2017-10-18T17:50:08Z", "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mythmon/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mythmon/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mythmon/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mythmon"